11070000.text:
[Recommended level] 61
I met Yoo Ae-rin, a member of the plum flower stalk, whom I met at Suwol Plain. Yu Ae-rin, who is completely excited to open up unexplored land...

11070001.text: [Recommended level] 68\nMaehwadan Yu Ae-rin appeared in the swamp of the abandoned this time. Does she have no fear...? Going out to explore alone in such a rough place!

11070002.text:
[Recommended level] 62
Steel fists saying that he has something to ask of me. 
I heard it was a very difficult request.

Why can't he ask Pungbaekmoon and Suyang for what they need, such a simple thing?

11070003.text:
[Recommended level] 66
Jeok Ho-young of the drugstore who is worried about running out of medicines from the Haewol branch. They say that they use temporary measures to overcome the situation...

The temporary measures he came up with were unconventional...!

11070004.text: [Recommended level] 71\nPungbaekmoon Sagilmi who wants to make something and hit the jackpot.\nWhat are you trying to make that makes you look so excited?

11070005.text: [Recommended level] 69\nTae-Su-Jeong is suffering from guilt for not being able to save the prisoners who were sacrificed to the Black Dawn. Her expression looks very empty.

11070006.text: [Recommended level] 71\nSeo-Hoon Mo, who has completely lost his temper, is gibbling.

11070007.text: [Recommended level] 75\nTae-Su-Jung and Jang Ho-Woon who want to build a grave for the victims.\nBut the shelter doesn't have enough money, so even that doesn't seem feasible.

11070008.text:
[Recommended level] 73
Carpenters at the shelter who are worried because the ax of Geumgyeongcheolmun hasn't been delivered. There's no way they can't keep their promises at Geumgyeongcheolmun managed by Moonlight Wind??

Something must have happened. How

11070009.text: [Recommended level] 71\nWhen I found out the circumstances of the case where the axe was not delivered, it was said that the deliveryman stole it. The liver is too big... To act like that with a moonlight-style thing!

11070010.text: [Recommended level] 62\n A zoologist named Park Bo-bak set out to solve the problem of dimness. But, this person... I think I've seen it somewhere...?

11070011.text: [Recommended level] 65\nGil Do-jeong, who introduced himself as Yo. Lee. Buy, has made a demanding request to me. The supply of food is not smooth, so I want you to find out what happened.

11070012.text: [Recommended level] 75\nI heard the stories of refugees saying that there were people who were struck by lightning?! There is a story that there will be traces left on the trees in the Black Dawn supply station.

11070013.text:
[Recommended Level] 68
Plum Manager The Red Plum Blossoms look very angry!!!
I think it's because of the parents who want to leave their children to the Plum Blossoms, and even say that they left their children in the forest...? 

How could this be?

11070014.text: [Recommended level] 62\nAmethyst, a member of the Poongbaekmun clan who is concerned about the future of Poongbaekmun.

11070015.text: [Recommended level] 62\nEunso Ha of Poongbaekmoon, who is looking for a training method to improve her own skills. Asked me to teach her how to train, and I ran to the Black Dawn's outpost.

11070016.text:
[Recommended level] 63
Steel Fist is complaining about the training status of the search corps. It's too shabby than I thought...

Steel fist with a confident expression.
